---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const links = [
  {
    name: "GitHub",
    url: "https://github.com"
  },
  {
    name: "Astro",
    url: "https://astro.build"
  },
  {
    name: "Hugo",
    url: "https://gohugo.io"
  },
  {
    name: "Vercel",
    url: "https://vercel.com"
  },
];
---

<BaseLayout title="友链" description="友情链接">
  <article>
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-[#111827] dark:text-[#f8fafc] mb-8">友链</h1>
    <hr class="border-t border-[#e5e7eb] dark:border-[#374151] mb-12">
    
    <div class="prose prose-neutral dark:prose-invert max-w-none prose-p:my-5 prose-p:leading-7">
      <p>一些常去的网站和朋友的博客。</p>
      
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        {links.map((link) => (
          <li>
            <a href={link.url} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-[#111827] dark:text-[#f8fafc] underline">
              {link.name}
            </a>
          </li>
        ))}
      </ul>
      
      <p>想交换友链的朋友，可以发邮件给我。</p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>